# ─── RudraOSINT — Environment Variables ───
# Copy this file to .env.local. None of these are required — RudraOSINT
# is designed to work zero-config against free public data sources.

# All scanners run in-process (no external SCANNER_URL needed). All
# other OSINT tools (DNS, WHOIS, IP, certs, BGP, threats, CVE, sweep)
# call free public APIs (Cloudflare DoH, IANA RDAP, ip-api.com,
# crt.sh / certspotter, RIPEstat, AlienVault OTX, NVD).
